org.team5940.pantry.logging.messages.events

Class WarningEventMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.team5940.pantry.logging.messages.Message
      • org.team5940.pantry.logging.messages.BaseMessage
        • org.team5940.pantry.logging.messages.events.EventMessage
          • org.team5940.pantry.logging.messages.events.WarningEventMessage

  • public class WarningEventMessage
extends EventMessage
    A WarningEventMessage is type of EventMessage that deals with warnings. Warnings are non-critical errors, but are still things that should be looked at. The type "warning" is added and if given a throwable it will also add the "message" and the "stack_trace" of it.
